								i’m a homeschooled senior and i do a lil bit of stuff for <a href="https://hackclub.com" class="underline text-[#4C4B46]">@hackclub</a> outside that. 
								i also like talking to my <a href="/friends" class="underline text-[#4C4B46]">friends</a> who you should all meet! 
								on this website, I hope to share my internet findings, and express my thoughts, ideas and opinions on various topics.  
							</p>

				</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>